   - **`prompt.md`**: Full specification (read earlier). Key examples: dragon-material sword + enchantment 8, damage 1000 → 400 (high-ench wins). Dragon + enchantment 5 → 700 (only dragon, full reimbursement, then deductible). Steel + enchantment 9 → 400 (high-ench: 50%, then deductible).

4. Errors and fixes:
